flowchart LR
    A[What do you need?] --> B{Control loop?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Use latest state API]
    B -->|No| D{Need ordered samples?}
    D -->|Yes| E[Use queue / multi-queue]
    D -->|No| F{Need image + pose relation?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Use syncer with threshold]
    F -->|No| H[Use simple reader for smoke test]
    E --> I{Multiple sample kinds?}
    I -->|Yes| J[Prefer multi-queue]
    I -->|No| K[Single queue is okay for probes]

